Package gov.nasa.larcfm.Util

Class StateVector

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.larcfm.Util.StateVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
OutputList
public final class StateVector extends Object implements OutputList
Captures the position and velocity at a certain point in time. This class requires the position and velocity are already in a Cartesian frame.
